      • readEncodedAndGZipCompressedData

        public void readEncodedAndGZipCompressedData(java.lang.String compressedData)
        Read data from TiledMap Editor layer. Decode it and the decompress it. Then twu-dimensional array of TiledObject is created. This method use Apache Common Coded library. url: https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-codec/ ######### THIS METHOD ONLY SUPPORTS BASE64 GZIP COMPRESSED DATA !!!
        Parameters:
        compressedData - (String) data from tilem map file.

      • readCSVDataFromString

        public void readCSVDataFromString(java.lang.String dataCSV)
        Read data from TiledMap Editor layer. Only CSV data are supported in this method.
        Parameters:
        dataCSV - (String) data from tilem map file.
